- Boto3 ELBv2 Client: https://boto3.amazonaws.com/v1/documentation/api/latest/reference/services/elbv2.html
- Boto3 Auto Scaling Client: https://boto3.amazonaws.com/v1/documentation/api/latest/reference/services/autoscaling.html
- Boto3 CloudWatch Client: https://boto3.amazonaws.com/v1/documentation/api/latest/reference/services/cloudwatch.html

